biocode.fims.digester

Class Worksheet

  • java.lang.Object
    • biocode.fims.digester.Worksheet

  • public class Worksheet
extends java.lang.Object
    digester.Worksheet class holds all elements pertaining to worksheets including most importantly rules and columns. Rules define all the validation rules associated with this worksheet and columns define all of the column names to be found in this worksheet. The Worksheet class also defines a LinkedList of messages which store all processing messages (errors or warnings) when running through this worksheet's rules.
